                </div> -->
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 col-md-12 order-1 order-lg-2">
					<div class="contact-page-side-content">
						<h3 class="contact-page-title">Contact Us</h3>
						<p class="contact-page-message mb-25">
							DigitranIT Software Solutions – Digital transformation technology,
							consulting and solutions implementation company with two decades
							experienced IT industry leaders. Our consultants with strong
							technical expertise in Pega BPM, Sales Force CRM, Full stack
