							and Google Cloud SAAS platforms, supporting the domestic and
							international customers during their business and technology
							consolidation, transformation initiatives..
						</p>
						<div class="single-contact-block">
							<h4><i class="fa fa-fax"></i> Address</h4>
							<p>
								DigitranIT Software Solutions Private Limited Parthasarathi
								Seeniammal Trust Premisis. Pudupair Village, Kundrathur,
								Chennai, 600069
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="single-contact-block">
							<h4><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Phone</h4>
							<p>Mobile: (+91) 73388 39489</p>
							<p>Name: Avanthika Sampath</p>
						</div>
						<div class="single-contact-block last-child">
							<h4><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i> Email</h4>
							<p>mail.ecrackers@gmail.com</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 order-2 order-lg-1">
					<div class="contact-form-content pt-sm-55 pt-xs-55">
						<h3 class="contact-page-title">Tell Us Your Message</h3>
						<div class="contact-form">
							<form id="contact-form" action="/contact" method="post">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label>Your Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
									<input
										type="text"
										name="customerName"
										id="customername"
										required
									/>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group">
									<label>Your Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
									<input
										type="email"
										name="customerEmail"
										id="customerEmail"
										required
									/>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group">
									<label>Subject</label>
									<input
										type="text"
										name="contactSubject"
										id="contactSubject"
									/>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group mb-30">
									<label>Your Message</label>
									<textarea
										name="contactMessage"
										id="contactMessage"
									></textarea>
								</div>
								<div class="form-group">
									<button
										type="submit"
										value="submit"
										id="submit"
										class="li-btn-3"
										name="submit"
									>
										send
									</button>
								</div>
							</form>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
